@Comment:	Chi was not enthusiastic about doing the letter writing task. He said he doesn't like writing. After writing <Dear Mr Carle> he said he had nothing else to say. Mot gave him a few suggestions , but he mostly worked on his own. He may have been distracted by the TV and SI2's interruptions. He told EXP that his letter <ain't great> , and that he likes to draw.
